ğŸ”» How to get the first million

the first number you need to focus on is $274
also, $274 is the number of sales you need to make for 365 days

$274 * 365 = $100.000  --> the result which is your first stop to a million dollars
    the formula which will give you your first six figures

so how do you make $274 a day?
    $5                          if you have a $5 product you need to sell at least 55 products per day
    $10                         if you have a $10 product you need to sell at least 28 products per day
    $20                         if you have a $20 product you need to sell at least 14 products per day
    $100                        if you have a $100 product you need to sell at least 3 products per day
    $300                        if you have a $300 product you need to sell at least 1 products per day

add a zero to your quantity and you have your first million..

