ğŸ”» Rule of 72
    A formula to know how much time is needed to double ur money

    72 / % Rate of Return = Years to Double

    Examples: Stocks: 72/10=7.2 years
              Bonds: 72/3=24 years
              Savings Account: 72/0.3=240 years



